[[File:Jug of water detail.png|left|130px]]
A '''jug of water''' is a [[jug]] filled up on a [[water source]] such as a [[fountain]] or [[sink]], it cannot be filled using a well. The [[humidify]] spell will also turn any [[Jug|empty jugs]] in the player's inventory into jugs of water. Jugs of water cannot be consumed, they are only used in making of other things, such as: [[dough]]s, [[jugs of wine]], [[soft clay]], [[mud pie]], and filling [[waterskin]]s.

A free jug of water can be obtained by speaking with [[Hassan]] in the [[Al Kharid Palace]].

One jug of water is required during the [[Monk's Friend]] [[quest]] to sober up [[Brother Cedric]].

The [[closest]] water source to a [[bank]] for filling many jugs is the [[Hosidius Kitchen]].

